        <label for="select-book">Select Book:</label><br>
        <select id="select-book" name="select-book" required>
            <option value="">--Select a Book--</option>
            {% for book in books %}
            <option value="{{ book.book_id }}">{{ book.title }} by {{ book.author }}</option>
            {% endfor %}
        </select><br><br>
        <label for="rating-select">Rating:</label><br>
        <select id="rating-select" name="rating-select" required>
            <option value="">--Select Rating--</option>
            <option value="5">5 stars</option>
            <option value="4">4 stars</option>
            <option value="3">3 stars</option>
            <option value="2">2 stars</option>
            <option value="1">1 star</option>
        </select><br><br>
        <label for="review-text">Review:</label><br>
        <textarea id="review-text" name="review-text" rows="5" cols="50" required></textarea><br><br>
        <button type="submit" id="submit-review-button">Submit Review</button>
    </form>
    <nav class="write-review-nav">
        <button onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('reviews') }}'">Back to Reviews</button>
        <button onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('dashboard') }}'">Back to Dashboard</button>
    </nav>
</div>
</body>
</html>
```

bestsellers.html
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Bestsellers</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/styles.css') }}">
</head>
<body>
<div id="bestsellers-page">
    <h1>Bestsellers</h1>
    <form method="get" action="{{ url_for('bestsellers') }}">
        <label for="time-period-filter">Filter by Time Period:</label>
        <select id="time-period-filter" name="period" onchange="this.form.submit()">
            {% for period in time_periods %}
            <option value="{{ period }}" {% if time_period_filter == period %}selected{% endif %}>{{ period }}</option>
            {% endfor %}
        </select>
    </form>
    <div id="bestsellers-list">
        {% if bestsellers %}
        <ol>
            {% for bs in bestsellers %}
            <li>
                <strong>#{{ bs.rank }}: {{ bs.title }}</strong> by {{ bs.author }} - Sales: {{ bs.sales_count }}
                <a href="{{ url_for('book_details', book_id=bs.book_id) }}">
                    <button id="view-book-button-{{ bs.book_id }}">View Details</button>
                </a>
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ol>
        {% else %}
        <p>No bestsellers data available for selected period.</p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
    <nav class="bestsellers-nav">
        <button id="back-to-dashboard" onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('dashboard') }}'">Back to Dashboard</button>
    </nav>
</div>
</body>
</html>
```

